				<div style="font-style:italic">
Taking into consideration I do a lot of soloing, play on a PvE server and play as Horde, Do you guys think I've unnecessarily overlooked some things, things that I should have ? Things that would make me do significantly more dmg, or be significantly more mana efficient?<br /></div>
			
